        <div id="stopped-working-after-macos-update">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <span class="label label-danger pull-right">Trouble</span>
              <h3 class="panel-title">Trouble: Karabiner-Elements stopped working after macOS update.</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
              <p>
                It's an issue of macOS that macOS update sometimes does not restore the running process state sufficiently after macOS update.
              </p>
              <p>
                Please follow the instruction to solve the problem.
              </p>

              <ol>
                <li>Restart macOS once again after macOS update.</li>
                <li>Reinstall Karabiner-Elements if restart macOS does not solve the problem.</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <br />
